title: Pranitha Subhash Official App
description:
Follow Pranitha Subhash through her Official App smarturl.it/pranithasubhash .Download the free Pranitha Subhash app now!
Stay connected to Pranitha Subhash on her official app.
Do fun things:
- Check out the in-app social feed for live updates and videos.
- Boost your comments with Superstars, become a Top 3 Fan, and be seen by Pranitha Subhash.
- Join exciting contests for a chance to win amazing prizes like meeting Pranitha Subhash, event tickets, and more…
- Watch cool videos.
- Follow Pranitha Subhash on social media.
- Listen to the FREE built-in playlist and add more songs from your personal library, Spotify.
Download the Pranitha Subhash app now and #BeSeen!
About Pranitha Subhash
Pranitha Subhash is an Indian film actress, model who predominantly appears in Kannada, Telugu and Tamil films. She was raised in Bangalore and pursued a career in modelling before plunging into films. She debuted as an actor in the 2010 Kannada film, Porki, a remake of Telugu film Pokiri, and in the same year starred in the Telugu film, Em Pillo Em Pillado. Her Tamil debut was with the film Udhayan (2011). She went on to appear in several commercially successful Telugu and Tamil films like Baava (2010), Attarintiki Daredi (2013), Massu Engira Masilamani (2015) opposite Suriya and Enakku Vaaitha Adimaigal opposite Jai. In 2012, she starred in a critically acclaimed parallel cinema, Bheema Theeradalli for which she was nominated for Filmfare award for Best Kannada actress and SIIMA award for Best Kannada actress.

title: Coloring Book
description:
The best way to learn while playing! 100% FREE content!
Over 130 funny drawings for coloring, scribbling, beautify and marveling with educational content, be a girl or a child, simulating use of paints, temperas and oils.
"Coloring Book – Kids Paint" is a educational game that encourages and helps your child to learn, develop and grow in an smart and creative way. In addition to amusing him or her, boost their creativity and entertain them positively collaborates in their growth and development.
This entertaining game allows them to learn to draw, colorize, paint, scribble, decorate, create and beautify very simply, just as they would on a paper, book or magazine, using different options to paint like brushes, crayons or pencils.
Children will be able to display all their creativity by coloring, drawing, painting and decorating their artworks with multiple stamps and graphics.
You and your children will surprise by creating and decorating incredible artworks with funny tricks, creating wonders, magic Kingdoms, stimulating their imagination, filling their minds with fantasy and adventures while reflecting everything in their exciting drawings, which they can share with loved ones and friends by WhatsApp, Instagram, Facebook, Twitter or email, among other options.
Their paintings, real artworkst, which were embellished by them with dedication and work will dazzle and amaze parents, grandparents, uncles and loved ones.
Coloring will give your child great satisfaction in realizing the beautiful things he is capable of doing on his own. It develops its capacity to discover, investigate and memorize. It will create drawings that will be valued by your loved ones stimulating your self-esteem.
This entertainment gives you the opportunity to express your inner world and channel your mood and feelings and giving you as a parent another way to understand them.
The drawings can be saved not only in their memories and dreams, also in the app for editing and continue at any time while they learn.
This application is ideal for parents, uncles, grandparents who want to "take care of children", "educate children" and "fun and excite" with a "useful and educational application."
The application works on both Tablets and Phones.

title: Coloring Book 2019
description:
The best way to learn while playing! 100% FREE content!
Over 130 funny drawings for coloring, scribbling, beautify and marveling with educational content, be a girl or a child, simulating use of paints, temperas and oils.
"Coloring Book – Kids Paint" is a educational game that encourages and helps your child to learn, develop and grow in an smart and creative way. In addition to amusing him or her, boost their creativity and entertain them positively collaborates in their growth and development.
This entertaining game allows them to learn to draw, colorize, paint, scribble, decorate, create and beautify very simply, just as they would on a paper, book or magazine, using different options to paint like brushes, crayons or pencils.
Children will be able to display all their creativity by coloring, drawing, painting and decorating their artworks with multiple stamps and graphics.
You and your children will surprise by creating and decorating incredible artworks with funny tricks, creating wonders, magic Kingdoms, stimulating their imagination, filling their minds with fantasy and adventures while reflecting everything in their exciting drawings, which they can share with loved ones and friends by WhatsApp, Instagram, Facebook, Twitter or email, among other options.
Their paintings, real artworkst, which were embellished by them with dedication and work will dazzle and amaze parents, grandparents, uncles and loved ones.
Coloring will give your child great satisfaction in realizing the beautiful things he is capable of doing on his own. It develops its capacity to discover, investigate and memorize. It will create drawings that will be valued by your loved ones stimulating your self-esteem.
This entertainment gives you the opportunity to express your inner world and channel your mood and feelings and giving you as a parent another way to understand them.
The drawings can be saved not only in their memories and dreams, also in the app for editing and continue at any time while they learn.
This application is ideal for parents, uncles, grandparents who want to "take care of children", "educate children" and "fun and excite" with a "useful and educational application."
The application works on both Tablets and Phones.

title: Doll House Cake Cooking
description:
Concentrate and be aware of each step because once you go through a procedure you'll be familiar with the next one. This game brings, beyond the process itself, the recipe that should you exactly what to do and even better you'll be guided the whole time because that is the best way to learn how things are done. So don't waste any minute and grab a big bowl where you'll be making the dough. Put the butter, the eggs, the vanilla extract, the white sugar, the baking soda, the baking powder and mix them all together to create that delicious cake. There are some important rules to follow and different stages that need a special type of attention and dedication, make sure you get through all successfully and look at the instructions so you won’t destroy anything. Such a sweet dish need your attention when it comes to details and assembling.
Use the oven to bake it and once is done, you can go straight to the decorating part where you'll be designing that colorful cake. Add a delicious glaze, choose the color of the dough and do not forget to put those details that would make your cake a special doll house cake. Make sure you accomplish all the given tasks because once you've done it you'll be able to cook it even better. Keep testing your baking skills and try a different design next time, also to forget to have fun while you baking this culinary masterpiece.
Test your abilities and seek the features we've presented in her in the game itself:
- Tasty syrups and sprinkles to add on your cake
- Improving or gaining new cooking skills
- Understand the importance of proper devices
- Introducing yourself to the baking world
- The opportunity to be a baker and a designer too
- Creating a delicious piece of heaven
- Learn the recipe and do it for yourself
- Free and easy to play
- Cool background sounds and graphics

title: Braided Hair Salon
description:
You have to understand why you are so important in this game and why you need to be fully concentrated for it. If you are passionate about hair or hairstyles you should love this particular girl game and not only because you will perform nice braided haircuts, but because you have the chance to practice your make up skills as well. As a starter you will have to go through 3 major phases that will complete your hair challenge. The first one is the hair wash followed by the hair style and the make up step. In the hair wash stage you will be make sure the hair is untangled and on the right length as the rest. Then you will have to wash it with some special shampoo and wait a required time to make the hair smoother and shiny. Dry it all out and then go to the braiding part where you choose the type of hairstyle do you like the most and then perform it very carefully. You will be  guided along the way so you don't have to actually worry for it. Braid the style you choose for the hair and try to do it in the right way, put one piece of hair on top or/ and under another so you could finish it. Now all that remains is to have the makeup part, but is not like a normal one, you will have to add accessories and make the  hairstyle look nicer and unique. Have fun and play more than once if you want to do more than one style of braided hair.
This is for sure a nice experience to have and the multitude of features this games brings are amazing, you can even see them detailed in this section:
- Easy to play also a pretty interesting gameplay
- Cool music and good looking girl to help
- Develop new hair styling skills
- Make new designs for her hair and try something different
- You will also have to own some makeup abilities in order to perform the whole game
- Free to play
- Many ways to see how a hair is actually braided
- Given instructions and easy way to accomplish the given tasks

title: Kitty Care and Grooming
description:
What a shame! This little kitten was lost and she seems to get into bad places when she was gone. She is totally hurt and needs you grooming right away. Offer her that treatment she really needs and make sure you pamper her a little bit, after all as a feline she is used to be spoiled and taken care of regularly. Get her out of the bush and take her in your home to be able to give her the proper groom required. Remove the foreign objects and clean the spot. Put on the substance that will cicatrize the area and let the healing part continue. Make sure the fur is all cleaned up and shiny. You should focus on the part where you wash the fur and arrange her hair. Apply the shampoo, rub it well and cut the hair that seems to stay rebel and messy.
Accomplish the spa challenges and keep going on with all the things that need to be done in order to please this little fluffy ball. Now you have to take care of the dressing part where you add colorful pieces of clothing and interesting accessories to make her look even more full of life. Put on colorful accessories, add a nice outfit maybe you could even try to combine the look with your personal style. You can have a lot of fun if you know how to handle this situation, be responsible and also try to learn the importance of a proper care.
Look at these amazing features this game provides for you:
- Looking after a sweet cat
- Offering her the care he needs to get better
- Use interesting devices to treat his disease
- Learning the importance of a good care
- Easy control of the game
- Free to play
- Developing new abilities in the nursing area
- Creating cool looks with multitude of accessories
- Peaceful music and cute designed graphics

title: AstroSage Kundli : Astrology
description:
AstorSage Kundli is No.1 Kundli Software (Kundali, Birth Chart, or Vedic Horoscope) based on Indian Astrology aka Vedic Astrology, Hindu Astrology or Jyotish in Android Market. Get Kundli, Horoscope Matching, Astrology, Horoscope, Rashifal, Hindu Calendar (Panchang) & much more absolutely FREE.
Features
* Vedic Astrology - Traditional Features
* Predictions/ Personalized Horoscope- Life Predictions, Monthly & Annual Predictions, Daily Predictions, Mangal Dosh / Kuja Dosham, Shani Sade Sati, Kaal Sarp Dosha, Lal Kitab Remedies, Debts, Planetary Predictions etc.
* Download PDF to Print Kundli
* Moon sign horoscopes - daily horoscope, weekly horoscope, weekly love horoscope, monthly horoscope and yearly horoscope
* KP System / Krishnamurti Paddhati with Significators, Ruling Planets, KP Ayanamsa, Nakshatra Nadi Coordinates and Sub-Sub Positions etc.
* Stellar: KP, Cuspal Interlinks (Sub & Sub-Sub), 4-Step
* Shodashvarga - All 16 divisional charts
* Shadbala, Ashtakvarga & Prastarashtakvarga, Western aspects,  Bhava Chalit chart
* Vimshottari Dasha / Udu Dasha upto five levels, and Yogini Dasha
* Panchang: Daily Panchang & Muhurat, Hora, Rahu Kaal, Choghadiya, Hindu Calendar with Festivals, Do Ghati Muhurat (Abhijit Muhurat, Vijay Muhurta etc.)
* Horoscope Matching: Kundali Matching (Ashtakoota Guna Milap or 36 Points Match)
* Horoscope 2019 & Calendar 2019
* Daily rashifal, monthly rashiphal, rashifal 2019, daily rasi palan and rasi palangal 2019
* Learn astrology - text and video tutorials and astrology lessons
* Large city atlas with thousands of cities, and Google Maps Support for finding city latitude and longitude
* GPS support for Prashna Kundli (Horary Charts) and Time Charts
* Store thousands of horoscopes that can be viewed at anytime, anywhere.
* North and South Indian chart style
* Automatic DST correction
* Choice of Lahiri (Chitrapaksha), Raman, KP, and Sayan ayanamsa.
* HINDI, English, Tamil & Bengali languages
* Support for AstroSage Cloud so that chart saved on Mobile can be opened from AstroSage.com and vice versa
* Double touch to show planet degrees on the chart (shows degree inside chart in case of tablets)
* Chart rotation: click on a house in north Indian chart and it will show new chart with that house as ascendant
* Tajik Varshfal (Solar Return with Muntha)
* Jaimini Astrology: Char Dasha, Karakamsha & Swamsha
* Lal Kitab: chart, varshfal, prediction for planet in each house, remedies, kundli type like dharmi teva, andha teva, ratandh teva etc. and much more.
* Colored chart
* User friendly UI with flipping screens
* Option for exporting chart, emailing chart or sending it via Bluetooth. Saved chart can be printed later.
* Moon sign calculator, sun sign calculator, love compatibility calculator and more
This astrology software is especially designed keeping mobility and instant calculations in mind. For example you can immediately know the Ruling Planet of any time, cast Horary horoscope while on move etc. There is no need to carry Ephemeris, Panchang, Tables of Houses, Tables of Ascendants, and Tables of Horary Numbers etc.
No app has so many Indian astrology, Vedic astrology and Hindu astrology features like AstroSage Kundli.
Tamil people will find jathaka, jadhagam, jathakam, rasi palan and jathagam here. Similarly, Telugu language readers will find telugu astrology, rasi phalalu and telugu jathakam here.
Note: AstroSage Kundli App requires active Internet connection.

title: Rainbow Ice Cream Cooking
description:
It is time to make some more amazing ice cream desserts so you can pass them on at a party and enjoy the look on everyone’s face once they take their first lick of it. The first thing you will have to start with is to mix the Flour and the Sugar in a bowl, together with the butter. Continue with the baking powder, vanilla and milk to get it some awesome flavours.
Grab a second bowl and start mixing the icing ingredients so you can have both of them ready whenever you will start to decorate the ice-creams. Make sure to also colour these icings with some food colouring in order to make sure the decoration part of the ice cream making game will go well and you will have some awesome ice-creams to show off at the end.
Bring out the cones when you are ready to fill them up with the delicious mixture and place them in the ultra-freezer to get them chilled as fast as possible. Once you see the timer running low, prepare to remove them as it is now time to get to the decorating part. Add a rainbow frosting on top and then you will be able to add all sorts of different items that will contribute to the aesthetic part of the dessert.
Make lots of ice-cream cones for everyone to enjoy, and also take note of all the amazing features that this app has to offer:
-Colourful environment
-Entertaining progress throughout the cooking part
-Freedom of choice when decorating
-Amazing combinations of ingredients
-Smooth instructions that you can follow flawlessly
-Great sounding background music to set the mood for cooking

title: Learn Magic Tricks
description:
Learn Magic Tricks is a free application with thousands of Magic Tricks videos to help you learn the secret behind magic tricks and learn to do it yourself.
Easy To Learn Street Magic Tricks Explained. Quickly Learn The Best Card Tricks And Coin Illusion Secrets Revealed Here.
This cool magic trick learning site explains how to conjure up many excellent easy illusions, amazing coin tricks, and group levitation secrets for card magicians. Revealing simple close up trick routines where you can soon find yourself learning the art of vanishing coins and shuffling and forcing cards as you master these powerful crowd pleasures.
Remember that even though you know how to do the workings of a trick, the real secret of a good magic trick is in the delivery and performance of the magic by the magician. This is something that will develop with practice and confidence and you can experiment with different timings, different patter and even by introducing a little lighthearted comedy into the act. It's what works best for you as an individual. Learn how to throw cards. Practice which patter you feel comfortable with to help you on your way to becoming one of the better pro street magicians such as Dynamo.
You have great opportunity to practice your magic skills in the field of coin and card magic due to the small size of these props. Easily carried around, they can be readily available to be used at any free opportunities or moments during your day when you can put in a few minutes practice.
Cards are especially good for performing close up or micro magic.
Discover and learn easy magic tricks and mentalist style effects. New easy confidence tricks and party ice breakers are here to be learned. You will find that this magic tutorial site is updated regularly and that the instructions are explained as clearly as possible. Make Good tricks your own conjuring learning magic school.
You can choose to view some of the many fun free magic tricks instruction videos showing you how to learn tricks using easy to find items such as cards and coins or even poker chips. These video lessons are added regularly and include many newly added favorites to learn. Check this illusion site regularly to view the frequently updated free content and sleight of hand instruction videos.
Most recent additions include the Cigarette To Bill Illusion in the bar section and the highly entertaining Calendar Mind Reading Trick which can be found in the Street Magic category, both these cool tricks are worth checking out.
The magic links section offers links to other interesting card magic and entertainment sites and suppliers.
There is even a page showing some of the easier tricks on the site entitled Magic Tricks For Kids as these may be easier to learn for younger magicians to learn or maybe even for grand parents looking for a few magic routines to impress the grand kids with.
This magic learning app is being constantly updated and we hope you will enjoy the tutorials and information available here to learn basic tricks and sleights. Should you choose to do magic purely as a hobby or even go onto a full time or part time career move such as a magician for hire? Maybe advertising as a wedding magician or doing close up work as a table magician in a restaurant or bar, hopefully you will find some information in this site, useful to you.
Disclaimer: Learn Magic Tricks Videos are fetched from publicly available videos in YouTube. Copyright for the videos belongs to the up loaders of respective videos or to the original creators

Develop your visual scanning skills with these mind games and have fun with these picture puzzles to train your brain. This is the best application to find out and search for the five differences in two pictures. Once you find five differences, tap the area on the screen to spot the difference between two pictures.

title: Crazy Mommy Busy Day
description:
If you think that being a mom is easy-peasy and you could do it without any problem, this girl game will make you think again once you play it. You need to be prepared for this kind of activity and this game requires all your attention and devotion too. Just because you are a staying at home mom doesn' t mean you are not going crazy with those responsibilities and tasks you have to accomplish all day long. The first part in the morning begins with preparing your little girl for school. Get that box for lunch and fulfill it with a delicious healthy snack, then add some chips and even a toast bread. The meal is ready, but you still need to help the girl to find her stuff for school and prepare her bag properly. Also, her school uniform needs to be put on in order to be able to go to school.
The next step includes dropping her at school and moving to the gym for some exercise to stay in shape. There are many types of movements you are going to do and each one will work on different parts of the mom's body. Execute them right and make sure you do the whole circuit in order to complete your training. Change in the cloakroom and be ready for a nice session of shopping at the mall. The coolest part is that you will buy new clothes and right after you will go to the supermarket to get the food that you need. Don't miss anything on the list and finish the shopping with the billing space where you will pay for everything you've taken. Have fun and see for yourself how is a day for a busy mom with kids that is trying her best to stay in shape.
There are so many exciting features this game is ready to offer for you:
- Free and easy gameplay
- Cheerful background sounds and cool graphics
- Have fun playing interactive activities with alongside a little girl
- Learning how to accomplish the given tasks
- Creating a delicious meal for your child
- Play different games all in one
- Becoming a responsible parent and stay in shape though
- Develop new skills or improve the old one

title: Princess House Hold Chores
description:
It looks like this princess needs a lot of help in this cleaning game. As you can see she doesn't come very close to keeping her room clean and in order. Your task in this princess game would be to refresh her clothes once with the whole room. The place needs to be all cleaned up and you have to be prepared for the challenges that appear. Begin with the cleaning part where you are responsible for each part of the room to look like new again. To be able to make that place feel like a home you have to remove the garbage and put each piece in the trash where the dirt belongs. Broken things need to be fixed and replaced, also the dirt from the ground needs to be removed using the vacuum cleaner and the mop. Then take off the spider web and clean the windows as well as the walls; the bed needs attention too. Use the tools you have and try to make each task in the way it should be done. Use the vacuum cleaner for leftovers and take the mop to the wet space. Once the cleaning part is done you just have to go to the next phase. The dishes washing is a little bit more complex and you got to take each plate and rub the dirt off it then wash it up. You also need to clean the sink because once the dishes are cleaned the dirt remains in there. Complete this stage too and move to the iron clothing. This could be a fun way to start learning how the chores are done around the house. Get the clothes and make them look like new again. Make sure you accomplish all the given tasks and at the end, the princess will be eternally grateful.
There are certain features this game shows like:
- Free and easy gameplay
- Cheerful background sounds and cool graphics
- Learning how to accomplish the given tasks
- Experience a wonderful gameplay
- New abilities to gain during the process
- Funky accessories and interesting styles to adopt
- Cleaning and designing challenges
- Variety of tools and processes to accomplish

title: Daddys Hair Salon
description:
As a dad, you need to make many sacrifices for your kids, but not this time because this makeover game will reward this awesome father with a relaxing day at a hair salon along with his girl. Be prepared for a treatment session that will be performed like in a professional salon. There is still time left to learn and find the secrets for a perfect hairstyle. No need to worry because you will get instructions along the way and you just have to follow the steps in a proper order. Begin with the dad's hair and brush it a little so you will be able to cut the messy strands, then you will find some dandruff and immediately go  to wash his hair. An oily treatment will be done at first because you need to smooth the hair. Wash it, dry it and arrange it while you take care of the edges using the haircutting machine. Style the hair with a colourful highlight. Now go to the girl and do the same, cut her hair,  put on a hair moisturizer mask made by you. Wash her, dry the hair and don't forget to create a unique design for her too. Next comes the dressing up stage that will let you find a suitable outfit for these two beautiful characters. Try something that will match the hairstyle and don't be afraid to use accessories like earrings for the girl or sunglasses for this cool dad. Have fun and find yourself a good fashion designer and an even better hairdresser.
There are plenty features that you could find in this game and some of them are identified below:
- Simple managing of the game
- Cool processes to accomplish
- Taking care of a sweet dad and his daughter
- Choosing from a large variety of clothes
- Having a bonding experience
- See how a spa hair treatment is done
- Learn the right steps for a cleaned hair
- Lots of accessories and interesting looks to create
- Free to play

title: Mommy Fashion Tailor
description:
It is time to have fun and you can have a lot by playing this new tailoring game that we have come up with. This mom needs your help and you will manage her wardrobe room along with the clothing from inside. The first task that will be assigned to you will be to clean the place and make sure that is a proper place for a talented tailor as you are. Clean the dust, remove the strains from the floor, repair the walls and wash after the leftovers. Then go to the tailoring part where you will basically make the material in a special shape using a pattern that will guide you through each piece of clothing. Follow the instructions given and make a beautiful design for the skirt and the blouse too. This mom will be pleased to know that you take into account their opinion. Crop, sew and put together all the materials needed to create a modern look. Pick the elements you like the most and then go to the accessories to tailor out the ultimate details. Be creative and use anything that will make this costume look better. When you are done you will be delighted to see that in her wardrobe will be found the looks you have just created. Put on all the elements that will make an outfit complete. Find the best combination and keep testing your tailor skills so you could become a great designer and fashion consultant as well. Do not forget to have fun because after all, this is a game that will offer you virtual experience and lots of joy.

title: Astro Guru: Horoscope & Palmistry
description:
Get an insight to what lies ahead for you with AstroGuru- A unique forecast app that provides you with astrological predictions (jyotishi) through free daily horoscope and palmistry . We offer daily horoscope prophecies and also for the entire week. With over 4 million downloads, AstroGuru is the sole exclusive app that gives you the best of palmistry projections by actually scanning and reading your palm. There's no better app for Astrology than us.
Know more about your fortune(bhavishya) based on your birthday(rashifal) and through your palm lines(hastrekha). AstroGuru uses highly advanced image processing technology for the calculations in all generated charts. Our predictions are entrenched with the ancient Vedic and Hindu methods of renowned Indian maharishis and pandits, just as Nostradamus’ were.
Are the astrological stars aligned in your favour? Will your career soar to new heights? Should you stay alert with your health? Will you have a happy married life? Install the app to know the answers to all your questions on family, career, relationships, money, marriage and more.
KEY FEATURES:
★ Horoscope & Astrology: Never step out unprepared with our all-inclusive, comprehensive horoscope that shows predictions for all seven days of the week. The app covers all twelve sun signs (rashi): Aries (mesh), Taurus (vrishabha), Gemini (mithun), Cancer (kark), Leo (singh), Virgo (kanya), Libra (tula), Scorpio (vrishchika), Sagittarius (dhanu), Capricorn (makar), Aquarius (kumbh) and Pisces (meen).
★ Palmistry: Unravel your fate by knowing the interpretation of the three major lines of heart, head and life in chiromancy. The heart line explains about love, friendship and marriage while the head line focuses on career, success, wealth. The life line gives an understanding of health and energy. Just scan your palm and let the app read your lines to reveal what lies in store for you.
★ Hidden Qualities: Each astrological sign has their own traits and nature that makes it different from the others. Learn about the hidden qualities in you based on your stars (nakshatra) and understand more about your strengths and weaknesses.
★ Compatibility Match: Confused if you and your prospective partner will make a good match for marriage? Want to see how well-suited are you with your spouse? Do they react differently than you certain situations- often more than a few times? Find out the traits of your partner's sign and see how well do your signs get along with each other.
★ Daily Quotes: Engage the mind and soul with classic quotes featuring authors from the ages, with wit, wisdom, and words that inspire.
★ Kundli:  The Kundli or Vedic Birth Chart is generated according to the positions of the constellations on the basis of the person’s birth day, time, year and place.
★ Languages: Available in over 20 languages including Spanish, Portuguese, Hindi, Telugu, Italian, Arabic, Chinese, Persian, Japanese, Turkish, Russian, Bengali, Norwegian, German, Korean, French and more.
The science of astrology can help you understand the kind of relation that is shared by the zodiac signs of the couple. Check the love compatibility between you and your partner based on your sun signs.  Matching their horoscope can also offer suggestions to mitigate the unfortunate facets of the relationship.

✔ Use the “Coat Hanger” button for chic accessories and makeup

description:
Make Joke of Creator helps you to create videos like one of the famous YouTube animated funny video Make joke of Creator (MJOC).

You can create your own videos with your group
Make Joke of Creator is free for creating videos and upload on social apps.

title: Real Talking Monkey
description:
An extremely interesting and fun app packed awesome features and fun games - Real talking monkey with fun games. The only Real talking monkey pet you can talk to & play games with for fun and entertainment.
Install the best Real talking monkey ever - The  Talking, Singing and Dancing monkey. He’s an adorable friend who listens & chats with you by talking through speech recognition.
You can ask him any question and he will answer you. He’s an adorable intelligent friend who listens to whatever you say and talks back to you. You can chat with him, play soccer with him,  sing with him,  dance with him, feed him, care for him and so many more.
★★Some features of Real talking monkey★★
- Take a picture using the camera or select any of your photos from your gallery and see the magic - Your face will be swapped with Real talking monkey and funny animations like snap lenses filters
- Talk and chat with Real talking monkey in the real world through speech recognition. He will listen to everything you say and talk back to you. He also serves as a virtual assistant to make your life easier
- Tap the mic to hear Real talking monkey sing.  In his funny voice, he’ll sing many songs like shape of you, love yourself, all of me, Hello and many more
- He can dance Salsa,  breakdance, top music, samba, Hip hop dances and many more. He’ll impress you with his awesome dancing moves
- You can play soccer with him. Just tap the football and play with him
- Poke Real talking monkey to draw a reaction like real talking parrot
-Make sure to feed your talking monkey so he doesn’t get hungry and sleep like real talking animal
- Take photos and share with your friends and family
- You can save edited pictures, record your screen and share funny snap videos and animations you create with features similar to snap lenses filters and snap face swap to share with friends and family. Do you love a talking parrot snap filter ?  This app also comes in christmas mode with funny talking santa animations
This is an extremely interesting app with awesome fun games. Get ready to be entertained with the best talking pet simulator ever. Not just a talking monkey or talking pet, this app comes with many fantastic games. Loved interacting with Thom, Ted and miss angel? Real talking monkey is much better than a parrot,  dogs and any other app on the market. It's a very great entertainer especially if you are into top games. do you love talking dog? This is the top talking monkey game and animal friendly app around, more than talking boy, squirrel and any other talking app with snap filters.
He is my talking monkey Noah but you can give him a good name like Thommy or any funny name. Your friends and family and can adopt and play with him or your baby.
Don’t forget to leave us a review :)

title: Clap For Finding Phone
description:
If you don't know where is your mobile phone - clap your hands loudly! When this app detects sound of clapping it turns on the loud alarm, so you will easy find lost mobile phone. Use your hands to clap loudly when you lost your Android!
How clap phone finder works?
1. Turn on our clapping detection service,
2. You can use your phone normally. When you will loose it - clap your hands,
3. Our service will detect sound of clapping and turn on the alarm - vibrations, sounds and flashlight! This will help you in finding your phone.

title: Chinese Food Recipes
description:
Test your ability to adapt to different situations in this cooking game where you will actually have to clean first to get to the part where you will prepare the food dishes. Try to understand how important is for a restaurant to welcome its customers into a nice and clean environment. The place needs a total restoring and you are going to make it. The floor is full of stains and water, the walls need to be rubbed, the main door made out of glass is full of dirt, there is a lot of trash around and the things all in a total disorder. Fix the chairs, get the place washed and don't waste any minute because you will need all of your time for the three special dishes that comes next. Go straight to the kitchen and find out how to cook these specific Chinese plates. The noodles are the first item and before anything else, you will boil them in a big pot. Prepare the veggies and fry them in a pan, add the chicken breast and the noodles on top. Mix the composition and once it is fried you will be serving a delicious Chinese food. Next comes the sweets and here you will put together some ingredients to make a dough. There will be the fortune cookies and others specific traditional meals. Follow the indications and make sure you complete three delicious challenges.
You can find them in a section of this game, but you can also spot them here:
- Free and really easy to play because of the guidance along the game
- Interesting gameplay and story
- Helping out a Chinese restaurant to clean its place
- Cool experience to gain
- New abilities to develop and the possibility to learn how to clean and cook
- Simply tasks to execute
- Become a cleaner and a good cook in the Chinese kitchen
- Delicious traditional meals to prepare
- Cheerful background sounds along with a nice interface

title: Vyng Video Ringtones
description:
Ringtones don’t have to be boring 🙅! Vyng brings fresh, fun, free video ringtones with every call! 💪💪💪
Instead of hearing the same ringtones every time you receive a phone call, Vyng plays 🙌SUPER AWESOME🙌 videos as your ringtone for every call! You can set a video as your ringtone, pick a channel to get a new video ringtone for every call, upload your own personal videos to use as ringtones, and set custom ringtones for your friends. Or you can just hang out in the app and watch hours of free videos - it's up to you! Oh yeah - it's free 😎
VIDEOS🔥
Browse video channels (including all of the best and newest music videos) then set your favorite as your free ringtone to get an awesome video with every call, including:
- Pop music video ringtones
- Bollywood ringtones (Arijit Singh, Akshay Kumar, Aamir Khan, Hrithik Roshan, Deepika Padukone, Ranveer Singh, Ranbir Kapoor)
- Hip Hop ringtones
- K-Pop ringtones
- Latin ringtones
- Musical.ly ringtones
- Electronic ringtones
- R&B ringtones,
- Country ringtones
- Punjabi ringtones
- Rock ringtones
- Dance ringtones
- Wanderlust ringtones
- Fail ringtones
- Cats ringtones
- Puppies ringtones
- Trending ringtones
- Fearless ringtones
- Phone Songs ringtones
- Dubsmash ringtones
- Acapella ringtones
- Good Morning ringtones
- Islam ringtones
- Reggae ringtones
- many more!
UPLOAD YOUR OWN VIDEOS 💃🕺
Want to personalize your ringtone further? With My Videos, you can create your own custom video ringtone by uploading videos (via the pink add button), curating your favorites from existing Vyng channels (use the + button below any video), or syncing with Snapchat and Instagram.
PICK CUSTOM RINGTONES FOR FRIENDS 🤜 🤛
You can also customize video ringtones so you get a specific channel or video when individual friends call you. Set a custom channel, upload one of your own videos, or ask your friend to choose the video that plays on your phone when they call you with Vyng Bombs!
WATCH VIDEOS 📺
Free ringtones are awesome, but if you don’t want to wait for a phone call to see an awesome video you can browse hundreds of videos across all channels with a single tap. New videos are added everyday by our community to make sure that Vyng always has the freshest and most popular videos!
Note:
- AUDIO: For channels containing quiet or silent videos, your traditional ringtone will also play.
- FULLSCREEN: Fullscreen videos work on most phones Android M and above.
- OFFLINE: Video ringtones will work even when you are offline! However, for channel content, you do need to periodically connect to the internet to get the latest videos.
Need a quick tutorial?
Visit http://vyng.me/faq
or contact our support team: support@vyng.me
Vyng uses your phone number and address book to connect you with friends.
Terms of Use and Privacy Policy: http://vyng.me/terms
Xiaomi users: please be aware that phones manufactured by Xiaomi, including some Redmi models, may not be compatible with Vyng. We're working hard with them to resolves these issues.

title: Princesses Cake Cooking
description:
Surprise the guests at the royal ball with this Princess cake baking game in which you will learn how to prepare one of the most awesome desserts they have ever tasted. The start will consist of you preparing the batter. This way you will have to use all the best ingredients at your disposal in order to ensure that the quality is nothing less than perfect.
Pour the sugar and the baking powder, together with the flour into a bowl and then crack open some eggs. Separate the yolks from the whites and proceed to add more ingredients together. You will be needing some butter to give it some smoothness to the taste, some salt to balance the sweetness and also a little bit of cocoa powder.
Take the mixer and blend all of these together until there are no more lumps left and everything is homogenized. If you do this step right, the batter will cook evenly and you will have plenty of fun decorating it afterwards as you do not have to repair any imperfections. Pour the batter into the cooking tray and then you will place that into the oven to bake for just a few seconds, as time flies by when you are having fun.
Once the base is complete, you will then move to the decorating station where you will have lots of icings and other treats and sprinkles that can go on top. For this reason, you will place each princess on the top of the cake and then begin to make them look amazing. Choose the right color for the cake icing, the perfect match for it on the sides as well, add some lollipops and all sorts of decorative accents that will make the cake look even more special.
There are lots of things that will impress you during the time you will play, such as:
-Hands on baking experience
-Plenty of steps to each baking process
-Accurate progression
-Freedom to decorate the cake to your liking
-Colorful and magical environment
-Beautiful soundtrack to set the fantasy mood
-Instructions that clearly remind you what to do

Pour the batter into the cooking tray and then you will place that into the oven to bake for just a few seconds, as time flies by when you are having fun.

Once the base is complete, you will then move to the decorating station where you will have lots of icings and other treats and sprinkles that can go on top. For this reason, you will place each princess on the top of the cake and then begin to make them look amazing. Choose the right color for the cake icing, the perfect match for it on the sides as well, add some lollipops and all sorts of decorative accents that will make the cake look even more special.

There are lots of things that will impress you during the time you will play, such as:
-Hands on baking experience
-Plenty of steps to each baking process
-Accurate progression
-Freedom to decorate the cake to your liking
-Colorful and magical environment
-Beautiful soundtrack to set the fantasy mood
-Instructions that clearly remind you what to do'

title: Train Cleaning and Fixing
description:
Make no mistake that this train game is definitely a funny one although you have to clean the mess and fix the broken things that are in this vehicle. Get ready for an exciting adventure where you will see the best parts of a train and how a proper cleaning is done. So use the tools you have and try to make each task in the way it should be done. Wet it, add shampoo, rub the dirt and dry it all. Wash well the smutty window, add the missing piece and handle all those scratches that are spread on the train body. Apply a special substance to get things all new again. Pain the wholes that are on the exterior side as well. When you are done the only thing that is left is the polishing phase where you actually finalize the aspect of the vehicle. Now comes the interior of the train that has some work to handle. Throw away the garbage, wash the walls, clean the carpet and make sure the seats are to the right standards for a quality train like yours. The repairing stage will teach you that the broken things need to be replaced in order to make your train works properly and as you like everything to be perfect you will complete the last part of the game. Look outside and inside the train and spot the things that are not working. Sew the scratched chairs, replace the carpet, put on new windows, have a new functional set of wheels, reunite the separated wires, add batteries and make sure each part of your train is working properly so it will be ready for departure.
This new cleaning game prepared awesome features and you could take a quick look at them right here if you want to identify them:
- Cool procedure to execute
- Possibilities to fix the broken things or to replace them
- Cleaning and designing challenges
- Guidance along the game
- Variety of tools and processes to accomplish
- Free and easy to play

title: SketchBook - draw and paint
description:
SketchBook for Everybody!
At Autodesk, we believe creativity starts with an idea. From quick conceptual sketches to fully finished artwork, sketching is at the heart of the creative process. You never know when a great idea will strike, so access to fast and powerful creative sketching tools is an invaluable part of any creative process.
For this reason, we are excited to announce that the fully featured version of SketchBook is now FREE for everyone!

title: 3D Piano Keyboard
description:
Piano 3D Keyboard
is the most popular piano learning & music discovery tool for the Android. Download now and immerse yourself into an unparalleled audio & visual experience!
3D Piano is a piano playing application on Windows with a 3D interface, effects, shading, bringing the same experience as a real piano
To own a piano you have to spend a small amount of money, especially the type of muscle, sometimes just stand and look. If you have ever tried the piano simulation software Piano 3D you can satisfy your love playing piano right on the computer.
3D Pianos Keyboard HD  work well on both tablets and desktops. It rearranges the audio with the ADSR filter that gives the user high quality sound. You can zoom in or out to see the full keyboard
Features 3D Piano Keyboard :
- Jaw-dropping 3D graphics powered by Metal
- Ultra realistic multi-sampled piano sound
- 3D Piano HD numerous piano instruments to choose from
- Huge user generated song library
- Music Composer: Write your own songs and share it to YouTube, Facebook or with other app users
- F3D Piano HD full on-screen multi-touch 88 keys keyboard with 3D Touch support
- Play the real thing on the 3D graphics platform
- 3D Piano use high-fidelity piano sound
- The library contains over 750 songs and the number keeps rising
- Audio bus support and audio in the application
- Simultaneous 87-key multi-touch keyboard and Android/Tablet display
- 3D Piano HD Decrease tempo whenever you want or pause and start learning each note again
- Switch to piano mode to improve the playing skills better and suitable for left-handed or right-handed players
- Built-in video recording, midi or audio recording (optional)
- Slow down the song at any time or pause it and start learning it note by note
- Switch to learn mode to help you sharpen your skills further and differentiate left hand and right hand
- 3D Piano HD built in Audio/Midi/Video recorder
- Full core midi support: connect your midi keyboard via Apple camera kit or any other Android supported midi adapter and watch your performance turn into 3D art
- Record on-screen performance and instantly share it to YouTube and/or Facebook right from inside the app!
- Midi Out/Virtual Midi Out: control any midi capable device and apps that supports background audio
- 3D Piano Keyboard integration using Inter-App Audio & Audio bus support
3D Piano models download , free Piano 3d models and 3d objects for computer graphics applications like advertising, CG works, 3D visualization, interior design, animation and 3D game, web and any other field related to 3D design.
In general, the 3D Piano Keyboard HD works well with a virtual piano on a phone, with smooth piano sound. A free application like Piano 3D may well be enough. Download the 3D Piano to play the piano on Android.

title: IMDb Movies & TV
description:
IMDb is the world’s most popular and authoritative source for movie, TV, and celebrity content. Explore popular movies and TV shows, entertainment news, and the latest awards and events. Track what you want to watch using your Watchlist, and rate movies and shows you’ve seen. Watch video – including exclusive IMDb Originals, trailers, behind-the-scenes clips, and more. Get showtimes near you, buy tickets, and read critic and user reviews.
Please note - IMDb is not a video streaming service. Full-length movies and TV shows are not available within the app.
Sign in to:
• Add movies and TV shows to your Watchlist
• Rate what you’ve seen
• Get personalized recommendations for movies and TV shows
• Save your favorite theaters
• Create lists to share your movie, TV, and celebrity picks, or make it just for you
Explore:
• Search our database of more than 5 million movies, TV shows, and entertainment programs, and more than 8 million cast and crew members, including celebrities, actors, actresses, and directors
• Read breaking entertainment news
• Browse quotes, trivia, and goofs
• Get complete event coverage from the Academy Awards (Oscars), Golden Globes, Emmys, San Diego Comic-Con, film festivals, and more
• Check out Best Picture winners, the top-rated and most popular movies and TV shows, and celebrity birthdays
• Receive notifications for the latest trailers, movie showtimes, and breaking news
Decide what to watch and where to watch it:
• Watch the latest trailers, IMDb Originals, and clips from movies and TV shows
• Check movie and TV ratings
• Read user and critic reviews
• Discover titles available to watch on Prime Video
Check showtimes and buy local movie tickets:
• Use your current location to get nearby showtimes
• Sort movie showtimes by start time, end time, genre, rating, and more
• Buy tickets direct from your phone or tablet
IMDb is available worldwide in English (US/UK), Spanish, German, French, Portuguese, Italian, Japanese, Korean, and Chinese.
Do you think we're doing something well? Is there something we've overlooked? Please post your feedback at https://getsatisfaction.com/imdb/categories/imdb_imdb_mobile

title: Talking Ben the Dog
description:
Ben is a retired chemistry professor who likes his quiet comfortable life of eating, drinking and reading newspapers. To make him responsive, you will have to bother him long enough that he will fold his newspaper. Then you can talk to him, poke or tickle him or even have a telephone conversation with him.
If you get Ben to his laboratory however, he becomes as happy as a puppy. There you can do chemistry experiments by mixing a combination of two test tubes together and see the hilarious reactions.
HINT: Record a funny video of your telephone conversation with Ben and send it to your friends.
HOW TO PLAY:
- Poke Ben's newspaper to make him fold it.
- Then you can talk to Ben and he will repeat.
- Poke or slap Ben's face, belly, feet or hands.
- Tickle Ben's belly.
- Poke or swipe Ben's graduation picture.
- Press the phone button and have a conversation with Ben.
- Record a funny video of your telephone conversation with Ben.
- Press buttons to make Ben eat, drink or belch.
- Press the chemistry button to switch Ben to the laboratory.
- Mix any two test tubes together and see the hilarious chemical reaction.
- Record videos and share them on YouTube, Facebook or send them to your friends and family by email or MMS.
This app is PRIVO certified. The PRIVO safe harbor seal indicates Outfit7 has established COPPA compliant privacy practices to protect your child’s personal information. Our apps do not allow younger children to share their information.
This app contains:
- Promotion of Outfit7's products and contextual advertising
- Links that direct customers to our websites and other Outfit7 apps
- Personalization of content to entice users to play the app again
- Watching videos of Outfit7's animated characters via YouTube integration
- The option to make in-app purchases
Terms of use: http://outfit7.com/eula/
Privacy policy: http://outfit7.com/privacy-policy/

title: Hungama Play: Movies & Videos
description:
Get the best of bollywood gossip, celebrity news, music videos, live shows, fashion tips & comedy clips at your fingertips to match your everyday essentials!
Hungama Play app offers curated, quick & fun videos to keep boredom at bay.
Watch it. Love it!
At Hungama Play there is always something new on offer, from Hungama Originals to handpicked content that reflects the spirit of the moment, be it seasons & festivals or trending artists.
We’ve curated fun videos for your five-minute breaks across Music, Hot Stuff, Filmy, Glamour, Spiritual, Comedy & Desi Kitchen. Make the most of mind blowing videos that you would love.
We have an extensive library of Movies & TV Shows that you can watch anytime, anywhere. Choose from over 7500+ movies and 1500+ hours of TV across English, Hindi, Tamil, Telugu, Punjabi, Bengali and other languages.
MOVIES
Pocket the BIGGEST BLOCKBUSTERS from Hollywood, Bollywood and other Indian languages, across-genres. Choose anything from a star-studded, to a critically-acclaimed or award-winning film. We have something for everyone!
Our BOLLYWOOD collection has the biggest hits of Salman Khan, Shah Rukh Khan, Ranbir Kapoor, Deepika Padukone and more, including super-hits like Prem Ratan Dhan Payo, Chennai Express, Tamasha, Khoobsurat, The Lunchbox, Haider & more. You can also choose from a variety of popular Bollywood classics like Andaz Apna Apna, Jaane Bhi Do Yaaro, Amar Prem and so much more.
Our HOLLYWOOD collection features the latest, popular and award-winning stars like Tom Hanks, Robert De Niro, Al Pacino, Ben Affleck, Leonardo DiCaprio, Dwayne Johnson; and includes super-hits like Kong: Skull Island, Going In Style, Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them, Batman vs Superman: Dawn of Justice, Mad Max: Fury Road, The Conjuring amongst others. You can also rely on us for any future releases.
Our REGIONAL MOVIES run the gamut from Telugu down south to Punjabi up north and include movies like Bahubali: The Beginning (Telugu), Natsamrat (Marathi), Thaandavam (Tamil), Nirbashito (Bengali), and Channo Kamli Yaar Di (Punjabi) etc.
TV
Enjoy a great selection of ENGLISH HINDI & TAMIL TELEVISION SHOWS and episodes such as critically acclaimed BBC content like Citizen Khan, Prey; as well as ITV content like Mr Selfridge, Beowulf & others.
Also on offer are POPULAR TITLES like Coupling, Mind Your Language, Top Gear and Tamil mega-serials like Vamsam and Ponnunjal.
ORIGINALS
Hungama Originals - Brand new stories for a brave new world. The first original series, Damaged, is India’s first ground breaking show about a female serial killer starring popular actors Amruta Khavilkar and Amit Sial.
KIDS SHOWS
Get the little ones tuned in to their favourite cartoons and shows – from Shaun The Sheep, Wallace & Gromit, Timmy Time to blockbusters like Storks, Brave, Toy Story, Happy Feet, Tangled etc.
SHORT FILMS & DOCUMENTARIES
Discover short independent movies and documentaries.
FEATURES & BENEFITS
* Now, Take your favourite entertainment offline and watch without interruptions – NETWORK OR NO NETWORK. You can also access videos stored in your device.
* Download Hungama Play and select from different plans and payment modes to access content on multiple devices with a single log in. Premium rentals are also available for a fixed period of time.
* Access video controls in the movie player with a simple touch and swipe
* Mirror movies to your big screen TVs using Chromecast
* Quickly access your preferred list of movies & TV shows by setting language & genre preferences
* Resume a movie & episodes from where you left off last time
* Add-to-watch-list helps you keep track of movies & TV shows you want to watch later
* Earn reward points (coins) that you can redeem for subscriptions or rentals
* Unique interactive discovery feature lets a user find content in a fun way

Hungama Play app offers curated, quick & fun videos to keep boredom at bay.

Watch it. Love it!

At Hungama Play there is always something new on offer, from Hungama Originals to handpicked content that reflects the spirit of the moment, be it seasons & festivals or trending artists.

We\xe2\x80\x99ve curated fun videos for your five-minute breaks across Music, Hot Stuff, Filmy, Glamour, Spiritual, Comedy & Desi Kitchen. Make the most of mind blowing videos that you would love.

We have an extensive library of Movies & TV Shows that you can watch anytime, anywhere. Choose from over 7500+ movies and 1500+ hours of TV across English, Hindi, Tamil, Telugu, Punjabi, Bengali and other languages.

MOVIES
Pocket the BIGGEST BLOCKBUSTERS from Hollywood, Bollywood and other Indian languages, across-genres. Choose anything from a star-studded, to a critically-acclaimed or award-winning film. We have something for everyone!

Our BOLLYWOOD collection has the biggest hits of Salman Khan, Shah Rukh Khan, Ranbir Kapoor, Deepika Padukone and more, including super-hits like Prem Ratan Dhan Payo, Chennai Express, Tamasha, Khoobsurat, The Lunchbox, Haider & more. You can also choose from a variety of popular Bollywood classics like Andaz Apna Apna, Jaane Bhi Do Yaaro, Amar Prem and so much more.

Our HOLLYWOOD collection features the latest, popular and award-winning stars like Tom Hanks, Robert De Niro, Al Pacino, Ben Affleck, Leonardo DiCaprio, Dwayne Johnson; and includes super-hits like Kong: Skull Island, Going In Style, Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them, Batman vs Superman: Dawn of Justice, Mad Max: Fury Road, The Conjuring amongst others. You can also rely on us for any future releases.

Our REGIONAL MOVIES run the gamut from Telugu down south to Punjabi up north and include movies like Bahubali: The Beginning (Telugu), Natsamrat (Marathi), Thaandavam (Tamil), Nirbashito (Bengali), and Channo Kamli Yaar Di (Punjabi) etc.

TV
Enjoy a great selection of ENGLISH HINDI & TAMIL TELEVISION SHOWS and episodes such as critically acclaimed BBC content like Citizen Khan, Prey; as well as ITV content like Mr Selfridge, Beowulf & others.

Also on offer are POPULAR TITLES like Coupling, Mind Your Language, Top Gear and Tamil mega-serials like Vamsam and Ponnunjal.
ORIGINALS
Hungama Originals - Brand new stories for a brave new world. The first original series, Damaged, is India\xe2\x80\x99s first ground breaking show about a female serial killer starring popular actors Amruta Khavilkar and Amit Sial.

KIDS SHOWS
Get the little ones tuned in to their favourite cartoons and shows \xe2\x80\x93 from Shaun The Sheep, Wallace & Gromit, Timmy Time to blockbusters like Storks, Brave, Toy Story, Happy Feet, Tangled etc.

SHORT FILMS & DOCUMENTARIES
Discover short independent movies and documentaries.

FEATURES & BENEFITS
* Now, Take your favourite entertainment offline and watch without interruptions \xe2\x80\x93 NETWORK OR NO NETWORK. You can also access videos stored in your device.
* Download Hungama Play and select from different plans and payment modes to access content on multiple devices with a single log in. Premium rentals are also available for a fixed period of time.
* Access video controls in the movie player with a simple touch and swipe
* Mirror movies to your big screen TVs using Chromecast
* Quickly access your preferred list of movies & TV shows by setting language & genre preferences
* Resume a movie & episodes from where you left off last time
* Add-to-watch-list helps you keep track of movies & TV shows you want to watch later
* Earn reward points (coins) that you can redeem for subscriptions or rentals
* Unique interactive discovery feature lets a user find content in a fun way'

title: Super Car Wash And Fix
description:
Girls, I have a superhero car. It protected me like a warrior last night in a big storm.Although I am unscathed,my car has been scarred and unrecognizable.The tires are leaking, the body is scratched,and the engine and battery are broken.I feel so sad that I need the best master to help me fix it and decorate it more beautiful.Girls,repairing a car is not an easy task.Would you like to work with me to repair my hero car?
Features:
1.Firstly, wash the car.Blow off the leaves and clean up the mud on the car.Then wash the car with water and wipe it with a towel.
2.Repair tires and mirrors. Remove the tires and repair the leaks. Smooth the scratches on the door and spray paint on them.Don't forget to change a new mirror.
3.The most complicated task is to repair the engine. First smooth the scratches on the hood and spray paint, then change the engine and fill it with oil. Finally,change a new battery.
4.The last part of the repair is the bottom of the car. Smooth the scratches,then find the damaged parts and replace them with new ones.
5. Now you can decorate the car.Tires,mirrors, tattoos,headlights, etc.You can change all the parts you like.
6. Next,we can drive to the place you want to take some photos.

title: Talking Ginger 2
description:
Ginger's Birthday - It’s time for some birthday fun!
Talking Ginger, the cutest little kitten, is growing up and wants you to celebrate his birthday with him. :-)
Join him for the best party ever - with awesome food and loads of games! Yes, you’re invited to hang out with the most adorable kitten in the world!
FEATURES:
- Talk to Ginger: Speak and he will repeat what you say in his cute voice.
- Play with Ginger: Cuddle, tickle or poke Ginger to see his funny reactions.
- Eat with Ginger: Feed him snacks or use the special 'meal time' button to eat together.
- Record Ginger: Record videos of Ginger having fun and share them with your friends.
- Celebrate with Ginger: Blow the party whistle for as long as you can.
- Play the mini-game: See how many birthday candles you can blow out before the timer runs out.
- Win free snacks: Get a free spin of the Fortune Wheel every 24 hours, or earn snacks within the app.
- Unlock rewards: Keep playing with Ginger to unlock more than 50 different jigsaw puzzle images.
This app is PRIVO certified. The PRIVO safe harbor seal indicates Outfit7 has established COPPA compliant privacy practices to protect your child’s personal information. Our apps do not allow younger children to share their information.
This app contains:
- Promotion of Outfit7's products and contextual advertising
- Links that direct customers to our websites and other Outfit7 apps
- Personalization of content to entice users to play the app again
- Watching videos of Outfit7's animated characters via YouTube integration
- The option to make in-app purchases
Terms of use: http://outfit7.com/eula/
Privacy policy: http://outfit7.com/privacy-policy/

title: Crazy Mommy Nursery Time
description:
There is no better way to prove that you could face a little baby than having in care three ones. This nursery game will challenge your patience and your ability to adapt according to a baby's need. As a mom, your baby comes first, but when you are handling more than you can you might have a tendency to go crazy and that is where you intervene. Give your help to this mommy and try to make a team while you are having three picky babies in your care. For the beginning, you will have to feed them with the asked food. But if you want to give them the required food you will have to provide it by making it. Each child will have a different taste so you will make three portions, one with carrot, one with apple and one with milk. Feed them and to unlock the tissues you will play a mini-game of finding the box. Next is the bathing process in which you will place two babies in the bathing tube and you will simply wash them with a little bit of shampoo and water. When the bath is over, take them out and dry them, but do not forget about changing the diaper. Next, will come the sleeping part in which you will be actually playing with four babies until they fall asleep. You will be using a singing elephant to proceed with the first nap, then depending on each baby need you will be playing, feeding or any activity that it will require for the baby to go back to sleep. To unlock some toys you will have some extra steps to complete, for the frog will be to assemble it, then for the milk to warm it. When the indicator for sleep is full the game is over and the mom succeeds in having a good care of these babies.

description_html:
b"There is no better way to prove that you could face a little baby than having in care three ones. This nursery game will challenge your patience and your ability to adapt according to a baby's need. As a mom, your baby comes first, but when you are handling more than you can you might have a tendency to go crazy and that is where you intervene. Give your help to this mommy and try to make a team while you are having three picky babies in your care. For the beginning, you will have to feed them with the asked food. But if you want to give them the required food you will have to provide it by making it. Each child will have a different taste so you will make three portions, one with carrot, one with apple and one with milk. Feed them and to unlock the tissues you will play a mini-game of finding the box. Next is the bathing process in which you will place two babies in the bathing tube and you will simply wash them with a little bit of shampoo and water. When the bath is over, take them out and dry them, but do not forget about changing the diaper. Next, will come the sleeping part in which you will be actually playing with four babies until they fall asleep. You will be using a singing elephant to proceed with the first nap, then depending on each baby need you will be playing, feeding or any activity that it will require for the baby to go back to sleep. To unlock some toys you will have some extra steps to complete, for the frog will be to assemble it, then for the milk to warm it. When the indicator for sleep is full the game is over and the mom succeeds in having a good care of these babies.

There are many features this game has:
- Mini-games along the way
- Great nursing experience to gain
- Helping a mom in need
- Bathing, feeding, playing, and napping activities
- Getting to know to take care of many babies
- Easy control of the game and free to play"

title: Talking Tom & Ben News
description:
Breaking news - Talking Tom and Talking Ben are even chattier and more entertaining as TV news anchors!
Join them in their TV studio, talk to them and watch them take it in turns to repeat what you say. Poke or swipe the screen and have them fall off their chairs! You can even create the news by placing your own video or photo on their TV screen!
You can express your creativity by creating the news or just enjoy watching the two tease each other. Either way, you'll have a bundle of fun!
Check out all hilarious animations by getting the full app now!
Features:
- Talk to Tom and Ben: See them take turns to repeat what you say.

title: Fantasy Ice Cream Factory
description:
When you are handling an ice cream factory you should be aware of some facts that might influence your final product and you will notice those only when you are going to manage it all by yourself. So, play this cooking game and find what challenges prepared you in it's following stages and try to solve each issue that might come along once you try to create a delicious ice cream. Because of your room where all the magic of creating and designing is happening, you must make sure that the cleaning is in the proper standards and if not you should take care of that. Use the given tools to wash all the dirt that might compromise your process. Remove the garbage, swipe up the spider dust, get rid of the stains that are spread all over the walls and floor, repair the nonfunctional devices that need a recondition or even a total replace. When you are done you will be moving further to the part where the cream for the ice cream will be made. Cut the fruits, turn them into a paste and use all those sophisticated devices that are specialized in making your dough perfect. Add colorant and different flavors so you will be able to serve a diversity of yummy desserts. Next is the cone making. Use the recipe and the ingredients you've got to make the composition then fry it to be ready to get that cone shape. Put the ice cream in them and don't hesitate to decorate each flavor you've got which is the strawberry one, the chocolate and the apple one. Have fun and make your factory work in the right standards.
You should check out these cool features this game provides:
- Free to play
- Easy control of the game
- Interesting processes to follow
- Getting to know how an ice cream is made
- Learn how to take care of your own ice cream factory
- Manage to clean the room where you will be doing the cream
- Find the way you should create the dough for the cone
- Decorate deliciously flavored sweets
- Check the steps and try to accomplish the given tasks
- Be a responsible owner and do the required assignments
- Awesome interface and lovely sounds

title: Animals Car Salon Cleaning
description:
Wonderful 3 cars that have animal's shapes are going to be your customers in this car game. Your car wash shop has high standards and your services are the best. So, this cleaning game has the main goal to learn you how bad exactly the cars looks like after some races and why they need to be reconditioned. The piggy car is coming first, and you will begin with the interior cleaning because once you finish this part you see the way the rest of steps evolves. Take the trash into the garbage can and offer attention to those speckled walls that need an immediately washing. Use the vacuum cleaner for leftovers. Besides all of that, you have to take care of the chairs that are broken as well. Apply the same treatment for the rest of the misplaced things and replace the windscreen. Now you have the exterior cleaning, so use the tools you have and try to make each task in the way it should be done. Wet it, add shampoo, rub the dirt and dry it all. Wash well the smutty window and use the tools you've got at your car washing magazine. Turn on the big device that will help you with the exterior and let it work until the car is all cleaned. Then dry it out and that is all that needs to be done. Now that you know these steps you might apply them to the rest of the cute cars that left in your garage, the elephant and the tiger car. Make sure you execute the treatment right because if you did it well the first time you don't have to worry.
This cleaning game prepared awesome features and you could take a quick look at them right here if you want to spot them:
- Cool procedure to execute
- Cleaning challenges for interior and exterior of the car
- Guidance along the game
- Variety of tools and processes to accomplish
- Free and easy to play
- Joyful music and pretty interface
- New abilities to gain during the process
- Lovely car in shape of animals to handle
- Learn the procedure for washing a car

title: Ghosts
description:
Ghosts & Spirits analyzes the readings of several sensors.
The complete equipment includes:

- Radar Map: draw in the city map the exact point of the detected energy
- Ghost Finder: help to locate focus of energy using gauss field (only in PRO versión)
- Ghost Camera: converts sensor readings into images (only in PRO versión)

title: Great Hair Princess Beauty Salon
description:
Get ready for this girl game and see if you can successfully complete this hairstyle braided challenge. You'll go through three intense phases that are about to change the way this princess look and hope for an improvement. The first thing you'll handle is the face and because of the stress and the latest problems she encounters, you will be having some work to do. Clean her face, remove the pimples, arrange the eyebrows, apply some moisturizing masks and don't let the dark circles get bigger. Once you finished that you could easily move to the next part and here the hair requires a special treatment and attention. When you wash the hair you will apply the special shampoo and rub it until the foam covers it all. Clean it, and then dry it with the towel and also the dryer to make sure all is done. Arrange it and choose the braided hairstyle you want to perform, then make it happens. Add suitable accessories to it and don't be shy to use sparkling jewelry. Now that you finalized this process, you can move to the nails. She requires a special pedicure and you will do your best to achieve it. Clean her feet first, then make a full treatment and designing. Choose the colors you like and be creative. Keep testing your abilities and try to add some innovative aspects to this princess look too. Don't forget to have fun while you play the role as a hairdresser for a princess.
You might look at these cool features this game brings you:
- Energetic music and awesome graphics
- Free to play and easy to play
- Choosing braided hairstyles for a cute princess
- Developing designer skills
- Spa treatments to perform

- Choosing a pretty hairstyle and create lovably pedicures

title: カラオケメモ
description:
カラオケに行ったとき、「次は何を歌おうか」、「この前歌おうと思った曲はなんだっけ？」と思うことはありませんか？
でも普通のメモ帳に書くと見づらいし、他のメモと混ざって管理しづらい！
そんな人のためのカラオケ専用メモアプリです。
オフィシャルサイトはこちら
https://karaokememo.shop/
公式Twitterアカウントはこちら
https://twitter.com/karaokememo?lang=ja
歌手名や曲名だけじゃなく、キーの設定など、カラオケならではの情報が記録できます。
「お気に入り」や「盛り上がる曲」など、自分好みのジャンルに分けることも！
正式な曲名が分からなくても、実際のカラオケ機種に入っている曲を検索して登録することも可能！
歌う曲に迷ったら「おまかせ選曲」でらくらく選曲♪
気になった方、まずはお試し版で！
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=itotsuka.karaoke_memo_trial
※お試し版からデータを引き継ぎたい場合は、管理画面の「データの引き継ぎ（機種変更の手続き）」をご利用ください。
質問、不具合、ご要望などありましたら、レビューにてお知らせください。
アプリ内の「お問い合わせ」からも受け付けてます。
★★★主な機能★★★
・キー設定
・タグ付け
・登録曲検索
・歌詞自動取得
・おまかせ選曲
・デンモク検索
・インポート
・バックアップ
・データ引き継ぎ（機種変更手続き）
その他にもテーマの設定や操作モードの切り替えが可能
★★★機能詳細★★★
【曲登録】
以下の内容が登録できます。
・歌手名
・歌手名（よみがな）
・曲名
・曲名（よみがな）
・タグ(お気に入り等)　※100文字まで
・キー
・レート(歌いたい度等)
・歌唱数　※99回まで
・メモ
【一覧ソート】
一覧の内容を歌手名、曲名、登録日等で並び替えることができます。
【まとめて編集】
複数の曲(歌手)のタグ設定・歌唱数の変更・削除ができます。
【歌詞の自動取得】
ネットワークに接続して歌詞を確認することができます。
※曲の詳細情報画面から確認できます。
【登録曲検索】
カラオケメモに登録した曲を検索することができます。
細かな条件指定もできます。
※独自検索システムを使用（以下「★★★独自検索システム★★★」を参照）
【おまかせ選曲】
カラオケメモに登録した曲の中からランダムで曲を選んでくれます。
条件としてタグや歌手が指定でき、一度に10曲や30曲選曲することも可能。
選曲に困ったときに便利です！
【デンモク検索】
ネットワークに接続して曲を検索します。
検索した曲はカラオケメモに登録することができます。
登録済の曲でもリクエストNo.が登録されていなければメモ欄に追加されます。
【インポート】
端末内に入っている音楽ファイルの情報を自動で登録します。
【最適化】
データ情報を最適化し、端末内検索や一覧のソート順などのデータ不具合を正しくします。
※同じ歌手が2つ登録されたり、曲情報の更新でエラーになる場合は、最新化することで解消されることがあります
【バックアップ】
カラオケメモに登録しているすべての情報をバックアップします。
バックアップデータは復元機能で使用されます。
【復元】
バックアップしたデータを復元します。
復元前に一度データが初期化されます。
【初期化】
すべてのデータを初期化します。
バックアップしたデータは削除されません。
【データの引き継ぎ（機種変更の手続き）】
機種変更時など、別の端末へデータを引き継ぐことができます。
みんなでデータを渡し合うことだってできます。
【テーマ】
黒と白の2種類のテーマが選択可能です。
気分によってそれぞれお楽しみください。
【表示モード】
アイコンから選ぶ「シンプルモード」
直感的に操作する「ノーマルモード」
2種類のモードをお楽しみください。
※以前のものは「ノーマルモード」としてご利用いただけます
【キャッシュの有効】
歌詞画面を1度表示すると2回目以降の表示が早くなります。
※端末の内蔵メモリ領域を使用します
【JavaScriptの有効】
歌詞画面で視聴などが行えるようになります。
※広告が表示される場合があります
※表示が遅くなる場合があります
【検索内容の記憶】
曲検索、デンモク検索で最後に検索した内容を記憶することができます。
いつも同じ検索をする場合に便利です。
【使用情報の送信】
登録曲数やソート順設定など、使用情報を送信します。
品質改善のため、ぜひご協力ください。
【最新バージョンのチェック】
アプリ起動時に最新のバージョンが公開されているかチェックします。
品質改善のため、ぜひご協力ください。
【よくある質問】
お問い合わせの多い内容が確認できます。
【お問い合わせ】
「よくある質問」で解決できなかった方や不具合の発生報告はこちら。
【友達に教える（シェア）】
以下のSNSやメールでカラオケメモを友達に教えることができます。
・LINE
・Twitter
・Facebook
・Google+
・mixi
・メール
★★★独自検索システム★★★
カラオケメモでは独自の検索システムを使用しています。
例えば、
「ありがとー」「ありがとお」→「ありがとう」
「しょーめー」「しょうめえ」→「しょうめい」
「バイオリン」「ハイオリン」→「ヴァイオリン」
のように少し崩した表現でもヒットします！
★★★ご注意★★★
データやキャッシュの保存には、端末の内蔵メモリ領域を使用します。
メモリ領域が少ない場合、メモの保存可能数が少なくなる事や、保存ができなくなる場合があります。
あらかじめご了承下さい。
★★★必須環境★★★
Android OS 4.0以上

title: Magic Flames: Fire Simulation
description:
Fire it up!
Magic Flames is a state-of-the-art realtime fire and flames simulation app and live wallpaper from the author of Magic Fluids!
- draw on the screen to create fire
- customize flames color spectrum
- use your own background
- adjust fire post-processing effects: glow, motion blur, heat shimmer
- save screenshots
- use as a fire live wallpaper or simply as a fun flame drawing app
Magic Flames is a true fire and flames animation app, based on fluid simulation algorithms.

title: Picasso. Bleu et Rose
description:
With the mobile application “Picasso, Blue and Rose”, immerse yourself into the start of the young Spanish painter's career. Throughout the sixteen sections of this exhibition, you will discover the stylistic evolution of Picasso, from "Blue" to "Pink", from Madrid to Paris, via Gosol, the small Catalan town in the Pyrenees, where he has lived for a period of time.
This ambitious overview gathers portraits, genre scenes, and poetic representations, and ends just a moment before the beginning of Picasso's cubic research around the Demoiselles d'Avignon (The Young Ladies of Avignon).
